---
// apps/site/src/components/UseCase.astro
---
<section class="usecase">
  <div class="usecase-inner">
    <h2 class="usecase-heading">Built for teams where “someone approved this, right?” is not good enough</h2>
    <div class="usecase-grid">
      <div class="usecase-callout">
        <p class="usecase-callout-title">Financial advisor marketing</p>
        <p>Compliance has to approve before client-facing content publishes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="usecase-callout">
        <p class="usecase-callout-title">Healthcare and regulated services</p>
        <p>Scheduling is allowed only after review, with a clean audit trail.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="usecase-callout">
        <p class="usecase-callout-title">Multi-site editorial teams</p>
        <p>Each site keeps its own users, workflow, and publishing boundaries without paying for a separate CMS install every time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="usecase-meta">
      <div class="usecase-meta-item">
        <span class="usecase-meta-label">Who</span>
        <span class="usecase-meta-value">Compliance, legal, editorial, and franchise-style multi-site teams</span>
      </div>
      <div class="usecase-meta-item">
        <span class="usecase-meta-label">Why</span>
        <span class="usecase-meta-value">Prevent early publishing, reduce workflow risk, and avoid per-site CMS sprawl</span>
      </div>
      <div class="usecase-meta-item">
        <span class="usecase-meta-label">How</span>
        <span class="usecase-meta-value">Self-hosted workflow + CMS on infrastructure you control</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.usecase {
  padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
}
.usecase-inner {
  max-width: 540px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.usecase-heading {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.usecase-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.usecase-callout {
  background: var(--bg-subtle);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
.usecase-callout p {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.usecase-callout-title {
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
}
.usecase-meta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
.usecase-meta-item {
  flex: 1;
}
.usecase-meta-label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.usecase-meta-value {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
@media (max-width: 500px) {
  .usecase-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .usecase-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .usecase-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
